{"lemma":"صاعِدٍ","slug":"صاعِدٍ","root":"ص.ع.د","root_slug":"ص-ع-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ع-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n24328"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D8%A7%D8%B9%D9%90%D8%AF%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n24328","headword_ar":"صَاعِدٌ","root":"SEd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ascending,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EunuqN SaAEidN","text_ar":"عُنُقٌ صَاعِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tall neck."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arafN SaAEidN","text_ar":"شَرَفٌ صَاعِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"High nobility"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b4-  [Hence also,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaga","text_ar":"بَلَغَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka*aA faSaAEidFA","text_ar":"كَذَا فَصَاعِدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It reached such an amount and upwards:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*otuhu bidirohamK faSaAEidFA","text_ar":"اَخَذْتُهُ بِدِرْهَمٍ فَصَاعِدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I got it for a dirhem and upwards;"},{"kind":"text","text":"an elliptical phrase, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*otuhu bidirohamK fazaAda Alv~amanu SaAEidFA","text_ar":"اَخَذْتُهُ بِدِرْهَمٍ فَزَادَ الثَّمَنُ صَاعِدًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I got it for a dirhem and the price increased upwards,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahaba SaAEidFA","text_ar":"ذَهَبَ صَاعِدًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went upwards:"},{"kind":"text","text":"you may not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waSaAEidFA","text_ar":"وَصَاعِدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", because you do not mean to tell that the dirhem with something more made the price, as when you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bidirohamK waziyaAdapK","text_ar":"بِدِرْهَمٍ وَزِيَادَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but you mention the lowest price that you offered, and mean that you then offered more and more. (Sb, L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraA^a faAtiHapa AlkitaAbi faSaAEidFA","text_ar":"قَرَاَ فَاتِحَةَ الكِتَابِ فَصَاعِدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He read the opening chapter of the Book"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. of the Kur-án]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and more"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a phrase of the same kind. (L.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}